column2: an A.M. Eatery////If you love pancakes this is the place for you. The cinnamon roll pancake is perfect on its own
column3: no syrup needed.Everything else is ok. My sister loved the breakfast tacos but they arn't really a traditional breakfast taco so I just enjoyed my pancake service this time was great! But sometimes it is a little off. They also have great gluten free options for the pancakes
